PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
John Coryell KELSEY, II, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 157940
COA: 329229 Supreme Court of Michigan. September 24, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the second motion of defendant-appellant to file a supplemental authority is GRANTED. The supplemental authority received on September 10, 2018, is accepted for filing.
